{"hb2240412g6964g452agbde0g426842982b70": ["You're still glowing from battle. On my honour, you've never looked more beautiful.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "ab5e05a3-47a4-2ea1-b183-510e2880d1bf"], "h1aacdfcdgab4dg4b5dg902egd25edab9113f": ["You're still glowing from battle. On my honour, you've never looked more handsome.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "ab5e05a3-47a4-2ea1-b183-510e2880d1bf"], "h5b526904geb17g4dcfg87ccg6a62ef8976a2": ["*You smell ale and smoke as Wyll leans in. His lips are but inches from yours.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "6dd05ee5-4894-a1c0-cce1-b8bf090cd8db"], "h844f6d18ge75eg4ba6g9c41gc02fc9db6821": ["May I?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "51b0c955-8072-24a7-a682-536c1e257b0d"], "hc3c000d8gd743g4249gaf3bg87517b87662d": ["No. I'd rather be alone tonight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "9981cda3-5f03-9093-7c92-c1b381554d22"], "h0db4a688g5267g4c13g8250gebff70967fd2": ["I understand.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "f29d16ef-40f8-28d4-e3a4-ca888847e34f"], "he66bc2e2g8410g4cd9gbafbgfaa881fdae93": ["I'm still a lucky man, I reckon, to have you battling at my side.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "bc33b29f-e1bd-1cb0-fb66-c787e0da39c7"], "hd7124ac3g9c13g4649gab33ged0411de53b2": ["See you in the morning, sunshine.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "e8059fe9-3c15-d88b-784e-ab0393f960c1"], "h1733f30fg6dbag4510gb631gf39faf6dec2d": ["Please. Kiss me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "072ae6eb-81b6-2c17-56d4-063bd52235fa"], "hdd3db572g02e5g41b8g9ca3gaf975c6970e3": ["*An ache grips your head. You see a flash - bronze hair, pale skin - and it is gone.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "02359972-f9e6-992f-7364-6526dfba835d"], "hb715a2e5g9f19g4551gabdfg753cfc50bdf1": ["Pardon - just a bit woozy. Now, where were we?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "d081f5e4-fd7c-5a5d-0dc4-6e3e9d65bcd7"], "hb0878900gec06g4723gb1c9g9deaf4942c60": ["*When the image comes, the pain is sharper than before - like a mind flayer scraping its claws across your skull.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "dbc8235d-b9e4-16d7-5665-9c9757f7c764"], "h4e75c0edg899bg4f88gadb9gad8f6815f742": ["*This time, you see a full face: a woman, skin pale as the moon, lips impossibly pink.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "6de1b348-1d7a-65ae-5958-a87ef0ef1f14"], "hbbf82712gd29eg4a6eg913fg4685979ad275": ["*But then she changes: pale skin turned to red; horns push through her hair. Her smile cuts through your desire like a blade.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "2a1d6570-5d8d-f5b1-0635-7c08b9e665e1"], "h8b4cc483gced0g4ba0g9943g093214aca50b": ["Dammit. Must she ruin <i>everything?</i>", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "1e8df667-c106-a4a1-ee0f-cbccfbf5adc1"], "hcd0b8742gfdeag407bgad47g59d5836db213": ["I'm sorry. It's not supposed to be this way.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "9d836366-ce71-0de2-85f4-5a1cd4df3844"], "ha8d2068fg4e5eg40abg82d2gbb332458ad8f": ["Are you sure it's really me you want?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "0c1d09a7-e0a1-30ab-c998-1c88c09e9256"], "hb789881egc26fg47f7ga800g1e5337953501": ["I'd give my good eye if it meant casting Mizora back to whichever Hell spawned her.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "a75f71b5-1781-9633-e321-576d70cbc8ae"], "h32a9f8a0ga30ag4004gaf69g1c355a8176fc": ["She may have gone silent. But she still haunts me - a ghost in all but name.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "6e86bdc2-ba14-dabd-9c05-e8617fba38a8"], "he1ed995bgcfc5g472dg8b70g854a6a8dfe7f": ["Sometimes, I swear I can smell her - sulphur and orchids. Stops my heart, just to think of it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "1acba2e0-a793-3039-5bcf-5684529669d2"], "h71ba8689gc112g417eg947cg0771cafbb74b": ["I reckoned I could forget Mizora - just for one night.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "2a47b446-c1c6-a731-a5cb-114c1f5887f0"], "h264b5fbfgd6cfg47c7g9cadgecc3cc06c60e": ["Gods, how wrong I was.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "a66c1ec4-d557-b9bb-a885-609c2781d733"], "h9a805744g186eg4176g8b7dg397de6163c35": ["Are you thinking of <i>her</i> while with me?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "c290afe1-e74f-6dfe-a1eb-14c3749ea666"], "h336a0f3eg1044g4c3fgb624g0d04eb2fb2d2": ["Is Mizora trying to intrude on us?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "12b7b1bd-d42a-af9a-23b7-ff95b647d240"], "h0f3afbf1gee65g482bg9204gb185ee4f3dfc": ["No. At least - not directly. She's not calling out, if that's what you mean.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "e0f06b55-e103-f697-91e4-40bf36598b63"], "h8dfa25aag6895g4d28ga26ag4341130bcd59": ["But wherever she's gone, she still haunts me. A ghost in all but name.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "8c702900-7df4-4a61-322d-cc4ae6085b28"], "hbc53be92g6fb7g49d7g9c3cgbfab3aee44bf": ["It's all right. I just want to spend the night at your side.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "33aa35b5-265e-e61b-d7bb-21a2b7b93524"], "hfa92b6eeg2a07g4631ga790ga08a5dd68559": ["Really? I'd like that.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "6b7f8871-73d9-31cb-cd05-ff9d2d0f599a"], "h6644ef4dge538g4f0bga571g1b92a7938ad8": ["*Wyll has slept next to you. He is still there when your eyes open.*", "NARRATOR", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "0c4a048c-3977-3387-6197-2671d2c13059"], "h4fb80b6cgae16g42fegb63dg2cd2ded3b5f3": ["You're more beautiful now, if you can believe it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "73831c67-a100-1d74-246d-1120a41f2116"], "hadcfc04dg3875g4769g9b8dg6dcca3c34a33": ["You're even more handsome now, if you can believe it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "73831c67-a100-1d74-246d-1120a41f2116"], "hf9099482g22a9g4e6ag8323g15ae16309def": ["That's sweet of you to say.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "00341342-f108-55cb-1112-3a3d365aaaa7"], "h45db8975g5990g46f5ga0a4g60be5f44f166": ["If truth be so sweet, friend, then let our words taste only of honey.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "35f104a4-f63a-1da8-e851-63b254ff871c"], "h4c8af9fege786g4533ga374g658d96c0e2d5": ["'Friend'. Is that all I am to you?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "7f324947-83cd-514a-5ea4-aa70afa3095b"], "ha979f689gd56ag483cg9010ga2f4cecdb444": ["Yes. But also - no. I've no proper word for what you are to me.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "1c6b292f-d5f2-2465-845c-c96ded771c5b"], "hca1ad7ceg484cg4eecg97bbgbd9f9ec7620d": ["Maybe we could do this again sometime?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "71649740-e134-072f-9033-75a765ccc335"], "h63e35fbdgb8a0g400bga0aagfb6d818dba71": ["We should get moving.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "4f038921-c2f4-c5d6-c36a-2a50e752ddac"], "h38825311gafb8g4b02ga64bgf4f0853f7fdd": ["You're quite handsome yourself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "dbb58aca-77cc-1c29-4740-7e046df47a83"], "hd8e081c9gbb2dg46dfgabd2gfc591b51ad20": ["You flatter me, friend. Surely a mere trick of the light.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "bf0f4176-f070-f719-c520-66c1b2dce42c"], "hd992f77fg22d5g4ce5ga9a0gc3fc81a7f02f": ["<i>Shrug off his comment.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "3d37f3c8-b576-eb4b-2894-abc2f8d56165"], "hc59c058cg1491g4571g9d21g5609398839c5": ["Ah - needing space, are you? Far be it from me not to give it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "d3433acd-5b63-bcf7-2574-c987ef2a9ed4"], "h4d20e36fg2f7cg42c6gbacfg834caaedbe1f": ["Up we go, then. There're monsters to slay, people to rescue, and all that.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "39fca8b3-80a3-fc95-d932-3591af7bd6df"], "h6bf6b571g6fecg4793gabc4gc5aad65ebfac": ["And... thanks. For everything. I won't soon forget.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "6213b427-4b10-108f-1e48-4ccfbd0d1b51"], "hfbf701e6ge36dg4d9eg81c5g9148500208d2": ["I had fun. Any chance we might do it again?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "9effeff1-b56b-b0c9-866f-2073e70d8a6a"], "h7685a9e3g2268g47c1gb87eg11b5f3adc7ba": ["A devil of a question that only a devil will answer.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "1aae332c-6020-368a-984c-56fd5cadb3e2"], "hbd48c75fgac3ag4b12g97cege9b455280863": ["I've never tasted fruit so tender as yours. But Mizora's eyes'll stray only so long.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "a027b6f9-2052-337a-32f6-d2b122cc733c"], "h005ccd67g5c2ag45a9gb17agd7f705e6c270": ["Only a free man can give himself fully. Until my pact is broken...", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "1d65451c-4610-6b92-8e59-f73bcaea8ef7"], "hdd1acbb7g65bcg4e78g98f6gbdc08644992f": ["... I'm never free.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "0f1c63ed-4838-de9c-237d-031a464c19f2"], "h9b35a814g530bg4c51g872cg4d7aee75543d": ["I'll help make it happen. We'll find Mizora and break the pact.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "68a204c2-c7dd-ca3d-bc34-436c9f85e070"], "h7eaaf690ge536g4126g96e8g2b453bd7fb89": ["You're a blessing. I hardly deserve you.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "0a0e75a0-676c-4859-0442-c5d00274fd8c"], "h21bf0eb5gf05cg4fedg8e7dg18b8f9da294b": ["Come, now - let's hurry it up. Legends don't write themselves!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "5e080b5c-61ad-9147-914a-25964e3d43c2"], "h928eab46gaf0ag42c4ga8ecg089571e3dce7": ["Mizora's a convenient excuse, isn't she?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "a3de1db7-4444-01c7-b5f4-6f295e3e90e7"], "h5cbd3d75g99a5g45ecg9a80g16914e0912be": ["Did you not feel my lips against yours?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "b6e8515d-d525-a957-4ebf-79b1a0f2b6c9"], "h5225d3dcgf81dg4db6gba27g15ed92ceec8e": ["Have you forgotten the <i>electricity? </i>Last night was a storm, and we were the lightning.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "7b71c2cc-186f-e8cd-1cd3-9469495d401f"], "hb797dc55ge5b1g4f21g93a2gc3b65c496403": ["Hand over heart, I will create thunder again with you once I'm rid of her.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "a35273db-6241-602a-8074-fbd42c413b80"], "hf3e954eage909g4a0dg889agb0be9d696ab3": ["Now come. We've much to do - and little time for it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "b5d3f1ae-e524-873c-87c4-533d6ded3aca"], "h5c94cfe9g3afag4028gae70g9d9e851f0ed1": ["We should get moving.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "07b62804-f66f-c38f-fe52-e5fce868f1eb"], "h4be26510gddb1g4028ga29dg435853948915": ["Come on, let's get moving.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "e083a7a1-c550-5411-4732-968c52ad5f42"], "h53cb29e3g9c25g4fa6g8c04gc3e9d21426d9": ["I'd forgotten what it was like to feel safe.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "1464e59f-c189-7d59-5d76-d75d64b24ecc"], "h7fc089a3g8e5cg42dcgacd3gaa4571748879": ["I'm used to being the hero.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "b72b7b2f-a257-287d-40d0-6a4b39601b7c"], "h6d7aef33gedd7g4f2cgaf64g9c9e2d7b0052": ["Not so used to needing one.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "9cd387d2-be20-94e1-2a9a-243b1b8a2c6a"], "h642e6ca7g938dg4321gb20fg3b7d52debfa6": ["You're still my hero, I promise.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "182cdacc-a5ed-11d3-cb3c-67d1bff1912a"], "h8f5fd718g6e1eg47d0g945fg2b2a7ae531e7": ["It means so much, to hear those words from you.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "8c11e1a4-6687-0309-5184-6dd477079cc3"], "h8b7bae7bge6c7g4a1cgb63dge77c959ebc7d": ["I wish I could give more in return. My flesh, at least. Something deeper, were you to ask it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "5e21238c-e5be-8ba9-58ab-75f366d7a2c6"], "ha47403b0g1156g4c1fgbc95g38b368a1fae4": ["But only a free man can give himself fully. Until my pact is broken...", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "1749078c-6526-1c03-4dc3-7cd155269573"], "hcfa5b430gf2b8g4634g9894g664bb5b8b51b": ["... I'm never free.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "76221157-bcc9-343a-ec4b-77ea3c68c0d9"], "he9353219g3487g4e23g9c71g32a66e53e517": ["I'll help make it happen. We'll find Mizora and break the pact.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "7873b02e-1b2c-946d-f585-4c2db34f1122"], "hbc27ad21g8fbbg43beg983dg80874bf0951b": ["You're a blessing. I won't soon forget it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "79bda46c-f440-48d2-f246-92ef6de07073"], "h6200dc65g1352g4d67g917dgb6f1eff02dc9": ["Now let's hurry it up. Legends don't write themselves!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "a81d0f53-7ed4-6626-ae5c-6f6eb7a71bde"], "h215c0443g0379g4800g9192g464ebae5534e": ["Mizora's a convenient excuse, isn't she?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "e6985629-09cf-f430-3a43-5dfb10f38681"], "h1ffe37d0g6a1fg4d95g8817ga5975bbf3d68": ["Did you not feel my lips against yours?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "a03f6cf3-b72b-75be-b0b3-09056cc5a7b7"], "ha5ed935eg761ag4f31g8085gc90084bea0eb": ["Have you forgotten the heat of our bodies pressed to each other?", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "1e8f1229-e782-c6be-0cd0-5f2aefd71956"], "hee9e04deg4bc8g43d6g8753g216f17ec06b7": ["Hand over heart, I would feel it again, and more still once I'm rid of her.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "25553a6e-719e-6303-1997-82f2c16feeef"], "h1addc8ccg152cg46dbgb801g110ca79ca2d6": ["Come on. We've much to do - and little time for it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "2bf487da-bf57-b1e7-acbe-65e2c2b097e1"], "hf77ff8a4g9289g4204g8db4gfe8a670004c5": ["Let's head out.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "6753947b-1a0b-7c00-857b-f86c4b58e4f0"], "hae2e0c17g2d15g48d9g8d52g3ca593fab351": ["I'm glad I could help.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "8ee1cafa-7e7d-2fd2-ca0d-e13322a945a9"], "hc159e032g94a8g44b8gbc23g8ba21a9c7956": ["I wish I could offer more than just company.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "8bc5217e-d21a-c523-24bd-2bedee746527"], "hc9ebdf50g6630g461bgb330g6431794bbd0e": ["My flesh, at least. Something deeper, if you were to ask it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "e80ca586-a4b4-f01a-e1da-1f2187e00142"], "hcbd35bdagd6cbg45bag8f9bga8bb7c8ef6f9": ["Do you suppose next time we might explore a bit more?", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "bb87ef06-8548-3bc2-4c1c-35cbef4468a3"], "hae4c8bc2gf361g4196g8e0egd4160ff1dccb": ["It's a good question. And I don't have an answer.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "ab045d40-fe7f-3690-eb96-bf3bd355228f"], "h02371747g4266g4f47g8c7ag8694e4e43d89": ["I thought I might at least share my flesh. Perhaps more, if you were to ask it.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "e3b8430c-e883-d96f-1679-0ee09a52d956"], "ha31c16a4gd5a1g4c79gaa5egb0f375a571ea": ["Up. It's time we get moving.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "aafed30f-f775-c216-24a7-388db2ad1244"], "ha481987eg353ag4985g8891gbab92fc8645e": ["Ahem - right you are! Monsters to slay, people to rescue, and all that.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "b5d175a5-61dd-bfce-e9fb-2944b4e4f1bb"], "h98c5cb0fgec99g493bg9be1g95e0f96a23e7": ["And... thanks. For everything. I won't soon forget.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "3aef6bae-dbfc-d2b6-6230-8d96f73ca197"], "h359ad870gbd20g4333ga724g0b353e184c8a": ["Hurry it up, now. Legends don't write themselves!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "3475b0aa-2d66-b67a-ed68-ba136e8cd46b"], "heef0d5a4g5187g4e62ga806gb9641564b26f": ["Last night was a mistake.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "860c227e-7e46-b08a-0443-0ee82b5b8bad"], "hfc6d64e0g5199g433cg9af3g36f4c74ee40e": ["Ouch. Not what I was expecting to hear.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "5b6f8d09-09eb-1ab6-bf7c-6fa531405278"], "h4d7b21bag67f0g4e83ga761g378fa6d5aad1": ["At least you were honest. I'd want for no less.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "537233a2-0190-275a-3533-6dba5b5d7e41"], "hdb6a829dgfc8dg493cga004gd49d25369e3c": ["Come on, then - hurry it up. Legends don't write themselves!", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "09bd0cbf-1c22-8d4d-6aa3-9d9919fca08f"], "h793d99f4g699fg43f6gb630g3c1b037f110b": ["Come closer. I'll help keep your mind off your devil.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "11a8fd7b-5cea-ba78-9554-69500aaaf328"], "hff546603g52f7g49bag8700g36468267d9d3": ["No. I can't.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "e0f870b1-6a2e-999d-dd59-7d6f9681101c"], "hd99b0f56g005cg4b96ga1b2g9cc1de3fe691": ["I just want you close.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "2e61695f-a69a-4b0e-e2b2-e48ed0f95c7f"], "h23089408g903dg4ea3g8f3dgd01299d78246": ["I'll hold you tonight. You're safe with me.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "345dcc85-31db-7c48-fb56-4c7ecfe811e0"], "hb9b57f2bg0745g462cg9c54ge04e8d7e5840": ["Fine. You can sleep here, just for tonight.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "f2326944-8f0d-a744-3f7c-e2b57d235874"], "hbb63f578g32c2g4a86g9934g32ef02a8880e": ["No. You should return to your bunk.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "b8de6785-7eab-5b29-4b77-fdf3abad4df4"], "hc6350b09g22bcg45a3gb03bgb4626b36da57": ["Please. Show me how.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "b48a733c-0613-4d6c-b99e-db1c47d4c812"], "hcf4ed0d3g980bg4734gacc0g8ca5e2a15b7a": ["Come closer. I'll help keep your mind off your devil.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "47e25d85-a2ee-c546-b192-ffad2a9d5972"], "hc526b340g9027g428bg9d49g3b42ded6cc0f": ["I changed my mind. I want to be alone.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "0276bfa9-53bf-a385-641a-d97093da27d8"], "ha8ca8c72g9bfbg469bga215g50ea2f57bb5a": ["I... I understand. Truly.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "0b12e85d-e519-129b-809a-d590314699a0"], "h431550bfg19c5g44fag893ag98e1df71563f": ["I'm still a lucky man, I reckon, to have you battling at my side.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "036a9cf3-5efd-77ed-143d-6d3fe94c0f9c"], "hbb10c722gc26eg44a8g917cgb1726faf4c7b": ["Anyway. I'll see you in the morning.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "4e5f7ee1-9a9c-b025-8423-bba3bc1f1545"], "h8f18cacag3104g4ee7ga514g01a641ea00f1": ["I am torn. I don't know that this is right - but I can't deny my longing.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "bde6060f-95f1-c4f4-b6ad-987673464f34"], "h371bfdb9ge2ebg478dgbeb0g86186c4694ae": ["You've heard it too, then - the voice of your wanting.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "63cb2213-9fc3-234f-6ac6-4a73c00780e8"], "h1cadb6c3g7388g4b35ga76agddb8c9e0f0d9": ["More powerful than any sorcery, more terrifing than any sword, for it speaks only truth.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "b83b0b43-54f3-0062-6030-07a2a57ad85a"], "hda81eb3egea64g4c13ga898g7fd3b66fd3b8": ["It is through wanting's magic that you know I speak true:", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "10ef7434-0f45-00bc-5243-3b28eb872d39"], "ha2b2140agba17g492bg931fgccba3315c9a4": ["I'm where I should be, and with the man that I want.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "d3d2537b-13f6-39a4-e5ab-ab36d9791e82"], "h64fc10bfga1dfg49adgaf7cg4f4913428dd4": ["I'm where I should be, and with the woman I want.", "c774d764-4a17-48dc-b470-32ace9ce447d", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "d3d2537b-13f6-39a4-e5ab-ab36d9791e82"], "h56944528gc78eg4a4eg8ea7g3abedf7b6ca0": ["Kiss me, Wyll.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "144fa58e-3547-b094-66ce-63c49f9dfad7"], "he7aec977g0c2bg4a48g8e83gae3f42a7634b": ["I've changed my mind. I don't want this with you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Camp\\Campfire_Moments\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_SD_ROM_NightWithWyll.html", "1c20cf22-fffc-14aa-9df9-a5b4e0a52cd3"]}